{
  "stem": "27409.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was sent first to Proskurov, that night to Proskurov, and-- [? how ?] [? would ?] you say-- all mostly Ukrainian which were called up, former Soviet citizens, and soldiers which came back from hospital, wounded soldiers which were sent back from hospital to the front.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I came to Proskurov, and there, we were sent with-- to a unit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The front was advancing near Brody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That is in old Poland, already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There it happened that we came about 7 o'clock in, uh, position.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I really did not know who is my commanding officer I had, who is my officers, company commander.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we came to the unit, and they told us stay here-- these were trenches-- to stay in position here.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were all armed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The most had passed a training of a month or two in Kiev.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was only one volunteered to the front, so I did not know the people around me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I could speak with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were Ukrainian or they are Russian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, uh, it was about 11 o'clock in the night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We heard firing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The Germans attacked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We counterattacked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was forest there, young forest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I got lost.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't know, really, where the front is, where my commanding officer is, where my colleagues are, my mates are.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I got lost.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I decided to wait till the morning for-- shooting from every side, artillery and machine gun fire.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I decided to stay there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "About an hour or two later, another soldier-- Soviet, in Soviet uniform-- appeared-- Red Army uniform-- appeared.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I joined him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We opened the [INAUDIBLE] it together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And towards the morning, a sergeant, Red-- of the Red Army-- appeared.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
